        Transforms a collection of transitions into a set of activities by choosing the ID of the given transactions as activity names.
        类型参数:
        T - Transition type.
        参数:
        transitions - Collection of transitions to get the labels from.
        includeSilentTransitions - Set true if silent transitions should be included.
        返回:

      • sanitizeElementName

        public static java.lang.String sanitizeElementName(java.lang.String name,
                                                   java.lang.String leadingCharacters)
        Sanitizes element names by the XML ID datatype standard. Names must start with a character of the range [a-zA-Z_] and must only contain alphanumeric characters and the symbols -_..
        参数:
        name - Name to sanitize.
        leadingCharacters - String to prepend to the name if it has not a valid beginning.
        返回:
        Sanitized element name.

      • validateElementName

        public static void validateElementName(java.lang.String name)
        Validates a given element name.
        参数:
        name - The name for the Petri net node. It must start with a character of the range [a-zA-Z_] and must only contain alphanumerical characters and the symbols -_..
